WEBVTT

00:00:06.480 --> 00:00:11.160
Honda's method involves placing Katayama
on the left, the ideology on the

00:00:11.160 --> 00:00:13.440
right, and folding the right flank.

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:21.360
Fold back the right lapel.

00:00:25.120 --> 00:00:27.280
With the front collar down.

00:00:28.080 --> 00:00:30.480
Align and layer under the right lapel.

00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:33.400
Align the collar points and layer them.

00:00:35.240 --> 00:00:36.760
Align the collar on both sides.

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:41.240
Fold the back neckline towards
the shoulder pad fabric.

00:00:44.680 --> 00:00:48.080
Place the left side over the right side.

00:00:55.840 --> 00:00:57.840
Fold the collar section to the inside.

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:15.640
Fold the left sleeve over
the body of the garment.

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:19.800
Fold the body in half.

00:01:23.080 --> 00:01:25.800
Place the right sleeve
over the body as well.

00:01:29.280 --> 00:01:31.880
This concludes the folding
of the tatami mats.
